data.description: Welcome home to the perfectly located neighborhood of Highland Heights! This cozy 4br 2 full bath home boasts soaring 9' ceilings, open concept living spaces and sunlit rooms. The 4th bedroom can conveniently be used as a study/office. The modern island kitchen includes warm laminate countertops, sleek black appliances, electric stove, ample prep areas, dark warm stained cabinets w/ plenty of storage. There is plenty of seating around the island or choose the breakfast area. The large primary bedroom provides lots of space and a welcoming soaking tub w/ separate shower for those quiet evenings at home. The extended, covered back patio is perfect for relaxing while enjoying the city views and backyard grilling. Local access to all the major thoroughfares, downtown nightlife and trendy restaurants.
